#

Creamy Garlic Mashed Potatoes

35 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Side DishComfort Food

Description

Rich and creamy mashed potatoes infused with roasted garlic for a comforting side dish.

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 2 lbs
  • garlic cloves: 4
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • chives (optional): for garnish
